      <t:profileDesc xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">
         <t:langUsage><t:language ident="en">English</t:language><t:language ident="gez">Gǝʿǝz</t:language></t:langUsage>
         <t:abstract>
            <t:p>A Gǝʿǝz poem devoted to St <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS6819Mary">Mary</t:persName>,
            which tells of her sorrow and distress caused
            by various tribulations the Holy Family experienced
            during the Flight to Egypt. According
            to the text, the exile lasted 42 months and ended
            with Herod’s death. It is chanted in the Liturgy of the Hours.</t:p>
         </t:abstract>
